OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1778054737
OL,3,CBoy arrested after police attacked
OL,4,Cwith petrol bombs in Londonderry
OL,6,FA 13-year-old boy has been arrested
OL,7,Fafter police were attacked with petrol
OL,8,Fbombs and masonry in Londonderry.
OL,10,FThe Police Service of Northern Ireland
OL,11,F(PSNI) said an investigation was
OL,12,Funderway to identify those involved in
OL,13,Fthe disorder in the Bishop Street area
OL,14,Fon Tuesday evening.
OL,16,FPolice said there had been a number of
OL,17,Fincidents of antisocial behaviour in
OL,18,Fthe Bishop Street, The Fountain and
OL,19,FNailors Row areas in the past week.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/5
