OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1778054737
OL,3,CBoy arrested after police attacked
OL,4,Cwith petrol bombs in Londonderry
OL,6,FA spokesperson said a number of
OL,7,Fpeople, believed to be youths, had
OL,8,Fbeen involved with some wearing masks.
OL,10,FPolice received a report at around
OL,11,F5.30pm on Tuesday that a number of
OL,12,Fmasked youths were gathered in the
OL,13,Farea.
OL,15,FA PSNI spokesperson said: "Bishop
OL,16,FStreet was closed temporarily to deal
OL,17,Fwith the disorder, causing disruption
OL,18,Fand fear yet again to the local
OL,19,Fcommunities.
OL,26,@wD@[OU
