OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1778054737
OL,3,CBoy arrested after police attacked
OL,4,Cwith petrol bombs in Londonderry
OL,6,F"A number of glass bottles were
OL,7,Fthrown, with fireworks also set off
OL,8,Fand petrol bombs and masonry thrown at
OL,9,Fpolice vehicles.
OL,11,F"A 13-year-old boy was arrested on
OL,12,Fsuspicion of riotous behaviour and has
OL,13,Fsince been released on bail to allow
OL,14,Ffor further police enquiries.
OL,16,F"An investigation is underway to
OL,17,Fidentify all those involved, and we
OL,18,Fwill take action against anyone
OL,19,Fidentified as committing offences."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU{D@cO]
